reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Loved it, works great I’m able to put all my important documents for my car in one place!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 12, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great buy! Fits perfectly
reviews.reviewText: Wonderful! Many people who come into my car think that it came with my car. It matches my car interior perfectly!! My middle console doesn’t have any space for cards - they would get lost in the hugeness of the space - so I had to think of another solution. This works perfectly and even holds my license and registration. Even though the leather doesn’t feel very quality (I doubt it’s real leather), it’s so cheap that I will definitely buy it again if this one breaks after a year.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: They’re very cute and I love the color, it matches my pink seat covers perfectly! The only complaint I have is that the straps were hard to stretch over my visors so they may not be compatible with all vehicles. I got them up there but they’ll definitely have to be cut off when I don’t wanna use them anymore.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Sun visor is just as pictured. Came quickly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really like the sunglasses holder, zipper pocket, and elastic pocket. The rest I have a slight problem with. They're just a little too big for, say, a credit card. So when you go to pull it out you end up stretching the pleather. Then when you flip the visor everything falls out of those pockets. Once they've been stretched it's too late. I wish they were more elastic instead. But over all I like it, it's a cute addition to my watermelon car theme.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Great price, great for phone, credit cards, pens, keys, etc. love it

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: 2023 Tacoma, fits snug and only use it for holding the discount cards for stores and a pen. Perfect for this type use. If you have a smart phone with otterbox, won’t fit, mine didn’t. Thin phone will without a case should would be fine. The sunglass flap, seems good, but I don’t wear glasses. The zipper flap looked fine and worked well. This visor is thin, and serves its purpose and seems well made. Just keep in mind, not made to hold bulky items like a bologna sandwich.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: A lot of people might say that this is a great thing and they use it all the time. I won't lie, I am one of those people. I love how it has multiple card holder spots, but do be careful if you flip your down, cause 1 might fall out in the looser pocket. It holds my registration and insurance card perfect and was really helpful when I got pulled over recently and had to get the information out quickly. I also use the pocket on the top for quick access to cash, which is helpful at a fast food drive through. All in all I give this product 5 stars, it's worth it.
Not even close to the item described see pictures for details. No zipper pouch TERRIBLE and cheap material quality DO NOT BUY!

reviews.reviewTitle: Great organizer, Cheap but it works.
reviews.reviewText: Exactly what I needed for my truck that has no other storage. Only issues I've found is that the material is thin, and quite cheap feeling with no stretch (so its hard to get much in the pockets), and that the sunglasses holder will only work for smaller sets of glasses.
